MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 1 : Increases Jump height based on Ninja Lair Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 1 : Increases Jump height based on Ninja Lair Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 2 : Fire and Smoke : Activating Smoke Bomb now triggers Shadow Stance.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 2 : Fire and Smoke : Activating Smoke Bomb now triggers Shadow Stance.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 3 : Increases the duration of Assassination based on Ninja Lair Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 3 : Increases the duration of Assassination based on Ninja Lair Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 4 : Wind and Storm : Stacks of Assassination increase move speed by 2% per stack.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 4 : Wind and Storm : Stacks of Assassination increase move speed by 2% per stack.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 5 : Increases the duration of the Slow effect from Smoke Bomb based on Ninja Lair Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 5 : Increases the duration of the Slow effect from Smoke Bomb based on Ninja Lair Rating.
